#: done.py:39
msgid "Is the student done?"
msgstr "Je, mwanafunzi amemaliza?"

#: done.py:45
msgid "Align left/right/center"
msgstr "Weka mpangilio: kushoto/kulia/kati"

#: done.py:132
msgid "Display name"
msgstr "Onyesha jina"

#: done.py:137
msgid ""
"ISO-8601 formatted string representing the start date of this assignment. We"
" ignore this."
msgstr ""
"Kamba iliyopangwa kwa ISO-8601 inayoelezea tarehe ya kuanza ya kazi hii. "
"Tunaipuuza hii."

#: done.py:142
msgid ""
"ISO-8601 formatted string representing the due date of this assignment. We "
"ignore this."
msgstr ""
"Kamba iliyopangwa kwa ISO-8601 inayoelezea tarehe ya mwisho ya kazi hii. "
"Tunaipuuza hii."

#: done.py:146
msgid "Problem Weight"
msgstr "Uzito wa Tatizo"

#: done.py:148
msgid ""
"Defines the number of points each problem is worth. If the value is not set,"
" the problem is worth the sum of the option point values."
msgstr ""
"Inaeleza idadi ya nukta ambazo kila tatizo lina thamani. Ikiwa thamani "
"haijapangwa, tatizo lina thamani ya jumla ya nukta za chaguzi."

#: templates/done.html:8
msgid "X"
msgstr "X"

#: templates/done.html:9
msgid "I have completed this"
msgstr "Nimekamilisha hili"

#: templates/done.html:11
msgid "Unmark"
msgstr "Ondoa alama"

#: templates/done.html:12
msgid "Mark as complete"
msgstr "Weka alama kuwa imekamilika"

#: templates/studioview.html:4
msgid ""
"This is a very simple component with no configuration options. It is used "
"for helping student keep track of what portion of a course they've "
"completed. For example, you might place this underneath each text and video "
"component, and students can see in their progress page which portions are "
"completed and  which still need to be watched or read."
msgstr ""
"Hii ni sehemu rahisi sana isiyo na chaguzi za usanidi. Inatumiwa kuwasaidia "
"wanafunzi kufuatilia sehemu za kozi walizokamilisha. Mfano, unaweza kuweka "
"hii chini ya kila sehemu ya maandishi na video, na wanafunzi wanaweza kuona "
"kwenye ukurasa wao wa maendeleo ni sehemu zipi zimekamilika na zipi bado "
"zinahitaji kutazamwa au kusomwa."

#: templates/studioview.html:6
msgid ""
"It is also helpful to give students a way to sign off on having completed "
"something. They are less likely to skip material that way."
msgstr ""
"Ni msaada pia kuwapatia wanafunzi njia ya kuthibitisha kuwa wamekamilisha "
"kitu. Kwa njia hiyo, hawataruka maudhui ya somo."

#: templates/studioview.html:8
msgid ""
"(If you're a real power-user, in OLX, we do allow you to add an align tag, "
"which can left-, center-, or right-justify the XBlock)"
msgstr ""
"(Ikiwa wewe ni mtumiaji hodari, katika OLX tunaruhusu kuongeza lebo ya "
"kuweka mpangilio, ambayo inaweza kuweka XBlock kwa kushoto, kati, au kulia)"
